# CLI-First Roadmap

- Before Week 3, prioritize CLI and backend pipeline behavior over dashboard features.
- UI work should remain placeholder-level unless required for environment smoke checks.
- New feature workflows must expose a CLI command or service entrypoint first.
- Keep API endpoints thin and aligned with CLI orchestration contracts.
